values: i havent been on this in awhile...so there isnt anything new on here...i hate josh...and i hate most all the guys ive talked about in this thing...i have a bf now but who knows how long thats going to last...grrr...i wish my life was simple...but its not...oh well...ill write more later...

Well there is this kid that i went out with about more than a month ago...and i seem to not be able to get him off my mind...i think about him everyday...and i REALLY want to get back with him...he is sooo cute...and he is really sweet...and i really wanna go back out with him...the only thing i dont like is that he has anger management problems...but he is really sweet...like u can hardle ever tell he does...unless u really piss him off...and i kno every little thing that pisses him off so i kno not to do that...and god if i get the chance to go back out with him i wont be depressing like i was the last time...i was sick when we went out the last time so i was all depressed and crap...but i hope i can talk to him tomorrow and see where that goes...because i do REALLY like him...and he is suppose to be going to Central High...which sucks...but i really hope i can get with him before that so that i can be with him...and if he goes to Central...oh well ill deal with it...i can still go out with him...no problem...he isnt the kinda guy to cheat on his girlfriend either...so i wouldnt have to worry about that...and i think he is like the sexiest guy in the world...god i cant get over him...everything about his is just so AWSOME...GRRRR...i want him so bad...

As I look at the stars at night and dream of what is to be... 
My heart begins to smile for it is you I see...
Knowing that you're close but yet so far away...
I dream of you at night and think about you every day...
For every moment without you seems like an eternity...
I dream of the day we kiss and I can hold you close to me...
So until that day comes you'll always be on my mind...
And I will love you till the end till the end of time...

OMG...this is the secong hurricane this month...the 1st one was Charley...that was suppose to hit my area really hard...but it ended up turning and not even hitting us...oh thank god...but this one is hitting us pretty bad...my neighbors across the street have it real bad tho...at least 5 trees have fallen down and the power line was about to break ealier...its just all crazy...and all the trees around my house are blowing like crazy...im actually a little scared...i mean i kno i shouldnt be but i kinda am...im worried mostly about my bf tho...i havent talked to him since ealier before it hit my area...so i dont kno if he is ok...cuz i was talking to him before it hit him...grrr...well i really hope he is ok...but im sure he is...

wow i havent written anything in here in awhile...so much stuff has happened...ive had a few bf's since i last wrote in here...i was with xavier for about 10 days and then broke up with him for a stupid reason...and i then realized i needed him more than anything...and i tried to get him back but he said he had a gf...so i then started going out with josh...and a few days after that xavier told me that his cousin pretended to be his gf because she was mad at me for breaking up with him...and he wanted to go back out with me...but i was with josh so it wasnt going to happen...then josh broke up with me because he said i was depressing...well im not normally depressing but when im sick i kinda am...so whatever he can go shove it...so now me and xavier are back together and i wont ever let him go again...i love him more than anything...he means the world to me...


~*~Ashley ~N~ Xavier~*~

well lets see...*he* came over yesterday...i actually had more fun this time than last time...i think it was because i wasnt as nervous...and because i really liked just being by him...i mean we really didnt do anything...we just watched secret window and hung out...but i was by him the whole time and it just felt so amazing...just knowing that he was by my side...just knowing that he was right there...i felt like i was perfect...like it didnt matter anymore what i looked like or how i was cuz he would always be by my side...(thats how it felt at least...doesnt mean it will be like that)...i dont care if my mom says that he lives so far away and a relationship wouldnt work...i DONT care anymore...i want him to be mine...i want to be able to say to my friends..."i'd like u to meet my boyfriend"...i mean i kno they are all just waiting to kno that he is my boyfriend...so im letting my mom kno when i talk to her that i am saying yes to *him*...cuz thats what i want...thats how i want it to be...i dont care if she doesnt like the profile...ive talked to *him* about it and *he* knows how i feel...*he* knows im not going to be like his ex...that im not going to be doing things like they did...cuz thats not me...im different...and *he* excepts that...and im hoping that even tho school will be starting up again soon we will still be able to see each other at least once a week...cuz i dont kno if i would be able to not see *him* for a long time...so im hoping soon *he* will be mine soon...even tho we act like we are already together i dont care...nothing will really change except that *he* will be my boyfriend...hehe...

i really wish that he didnt have to work tonight...i wish he was here with me wayching fireworks...im sitting here at my aunts house and there are all these wonderful fireworks going on all around her house and i mean there amazing but the whole time the only thing im thinking about is him...just wanting him here with me...wanting to spend time with him...well i guess that i will just have to wait til tomorrow to see him...altho i wish it was now...i wonder what movie im gonna be watching with him tomorrow...i guess i will find out tomorrow when we go to pick out a movie...well cant wait...almost there...YAY...*bites*...lol...

i sit here day after day just thinking to myself...
sometimes talking on the phone with people...
most of the time just listening to music...
other times playing a game...
but im just thinking...
thinking about all types of things...
family...friends...guys...objects...
ive been told tho...
i think about things i shouldnt spend my time thinking about...
well what if i want to...
i think about things like...
how my mom controls so much of my life...
how my friends just left me here...
how my friends no longer call me anymore just to say hi...
like i dont exist to them anymore...
how i cant seem to have a bf even tho i want one...
how i love the songs i listen to...
lol...that was a dumb thought...
i enjoy sitting here day after day thinking about some odd things...
